  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000044",
    "sentence": "然德化未流洽者，禮樂未具，群下無所誦說，而庠序尚未設之故也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000045",
    "sentence": "孔子曰：「辟如為山，未成一匱，止，吾止也。」今叔孫通所撰禮儀，與律令同錄，臧於理官，法家又復不傳。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000046",
    "sentence": "漢典寢而不著，民臣莫有言者。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000047",
    "sentence": "又通沒之後，河間獻王采禮樂古事，稍稍增輯，至五百餘篇。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000048",
    "sentence": "今學者不能昭見，但推士禮以及天子，說義又頗謬異，故君臣長幼交接之道娅以不章。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000049",
    "sentence": "樂者，聖人之所樂也，而可以善民心。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000050",
    "sentence": "其感人深，其移風易俗易，故先王著其教焉。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000051",
    "sentence": "夫民有血氣心知之性，而無哀樂喜怒之常，應感而動，然後心術形焉。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000052",
    "sentence": "是以纖微虍瘁一作「衰」之音作，而民思憂；闡諧嫚易之音作，而民康樂；麤厲猛奮之音作，而民剛毅；廉直正誠之音作，而民肅敬；寬裕和順之音作，而民慈愛；流辟邪散之音作，而民淫亂。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000053",
    "sentence": "先王恥其亂也，故制雅頌之聲，本之情性，稽之度數，制之禮儀，合生氣之和，導五常之行，使之陽而不散，陰而不集，剛氣不怒，柔氣不懾，四暢交於中，而發作於外，皆安其位而不相奪也，足以感動人之善心而，不使邪氣得接焉，是先王立樂之方也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000054",
    "sentence": "王者未作樂之時，因先王之樂以教化百姓，說樂其俗，然後改作，以章功德。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000055",
    "sentence": "《易》曰：「先王以作樂崇德，殷薦之上帝，以配祖考。」昔黃帝作咸池，顓頊作六莖，帝嚳作五英，堯作大章，舜作招，禹作夏，湯作濩，武王作武，周公作勺。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "《易》",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 3
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000056",
    "sentence": "勺，言能勺先祖之道也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000057",
    "sentence": "武，言以功定天下也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000058",
    "sentence": "濩，言救民也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000059",
    "sentence": "夏，大承二帝也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000060",
    "sentence": "招，繼堯也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000061",
    "sentence": "大章，章之也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000062",
    "sentence": "五英，英華茂也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000063",
    "sentence": "六莖，及根莖也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000064",
    "sentence": "咸池，備矣。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000065",
    "sentence": "自夏以往，其流不可聞已，殷頌猶有存者。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000066",
    "sentence": "周詩既備，而其器用張陳，周官具焉。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000067",
    "sentence": "典者自卿大夫師瞽以下，皆選有道德之人，朝夕習業，以教國子。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "大夫",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 4,
        "end": 6
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000068",
    "sentence": "國子者，卿大夫之子弟也。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "大夫",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 5,
        "end": 7
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000069",
    "sentence": "皆學歌九德，誦六詩，習六舞、五聲、八音之和。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000070",
    "sentence": "故帝舜命夔曰：「女典樂，教冑子，直而溫，寬而栗，剛而無虐，簡而無敖。詩言志，歌詠言，聲依詠，律和聲，八音克諧。」此之謂也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000071",
    "sentence": "又以外賞諸侯德盛而教尊者。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000072",
    "sentence": "其威儀足以充目，音聲足以動耳，詩語足以感心，故聞其音而德和，省其詩而志正，論其數而法立。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000073",
    "sentence": "是以薦之郊廟則鬼神饗，作之朝廷則群臣和，立之學官則萬民協。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000074",
    "sentence": "聽者無不虛己竦神，說而承流，是以海內遍知上德，被服其風，光煇日新，化上遷善，而不知所以然，至於萬物不夭，天地順而嘉應降。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000075",
    "sentence": "故《詩》曰：「鐘鼓鍠鍠，磬管鏘鏘，降福穰穰。」《書》云：「擊石拊石，百獸率舞。」鳥獸且猶感應，而況於人乎？",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "《詩》",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 1,
        "end": 4
      },
      {
        "text": "《書》",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 23,
        "end": 26
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000076",
    "sentence": "況於鬼神乎？",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000077",
    "sentence": "故樂者，聖人之所以感天地，通神明，安萬民，成性類者也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000078",
    "sentence": "然自雅頌之興，而所承衰亂之音猶在，是謂淫過凶嫚之聲，為設禁焉。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000079",
    "sentence": "世衰民散，小人乘君子，心耳淺薄，則邪勝正。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000080",
    "sentence": "故書序「殷紂斷棄先祖之樂，乃作淫聲，用變亂正聲，以說婦人。」樂官師瞽抱其器而奔散，或適諸侯，或入河海。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000081",
    "sentence": "夫樂本情性，浹肌膚而臧骨髓，雖經乎千載，其遺風餘烈尚猶不絕。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000082",
    "sentence": "至春秋時，陳公子完奔齊。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000083",
    "sentence": "陳，舜之後，招樂存焉。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000084",
    "sentence": "故孔子適齊聞招，三月不知肉味，曰「不圖為樂之至於斯！」美之甚也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000085",
    "sentence": "周道始缺，怨刺之詩起。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000086",
    "sentence": "王澤既竭，而詩不能作。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000087",
    "sentence": "王官失業，雅頌相錯，孔子論而定之，故曰：「吾自衛反魯，然後樂正，雅頌各得其所。」是時，周室大壞，諸侯恣行，設兩觀，乘大路。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000088",
    "sentence": "陪臣管仲、季氏之屬，三歸雍徹，八佾舞廷。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000089",
    "sentence": "制度遂壞，陵夷而不反，桑間、濮上，鄭、衛、宋、趙之聲並出，內則致疾損壽，外則亂政傷民。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000090",
    "sentence": "巧偽因而飾之，以營亂富貴之耳目。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000091",
    "sentence": "庶人以求利，列國以相間。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000092",
    "sentence": "故秦穆遺戎而由余去，齊人餽魯而孔子行。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000093",
    "sentence": "至於六國，魏文侯最為好古，而謂子夏曰：「寡人聽古樂則欲寐，及聞鄭、衛，余不知倦焉。」子夏辭而辨之，終不見納，自此禮樂喪矣。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000094",
    "sentence": "漢興，樂家有制氏，以雅樂聲律世世在大樂官，但能紀其鏗鎗鼓舞，而不能言其義。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000095",
    "sentence": "高祖時，叔孫通因秦樂人制宗廟樂。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000096",
    "sentence": "大祝迎神于廟門，奏嘉至，猶古降神之樂也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000097",
    "sentence": "皇帝入廟門，奏永至，以為行步之節，猶古采薺、肆夏也。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "皇帝",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 2
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000098",
    "sentence": "乾豆上，奏登歌，獨上歌，不以筦弦亂人聲，欲在位者遍聞之，猶古清廟之歌也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000099",
    "sentence": "登歌再終，下奏休成之樂，美神明既饗也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000100",
    "sentence": "皇帝就酒東廂，坐定，奏永安之樂，美禮已成也。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "皇帝",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 2
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000101",
    "sentence": "又有房中祠樂，高祖唐山夫人所作也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000102",
    "sentence": "周有房中樂，至秦名曰壽人。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000103",
    "sentence": "凡樂，樂其所生，禮不忘本。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000104",
    "sentence": "高祖樂楚聲，故房中樂楚聲也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000105",
    "sentence": "孝惠二年，使樂府令夏侯寬備其簫管，更名曰安世樂。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "二年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 2,
        "end": 4
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000106",
    "sentence": "高祖廟奏武德、文始、五行之舞；孝文廟奏昭德、文始、四時、五行之舞；孝武廟奏盛德、文始、四時、五行之舞。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000107",
    "sentence": "武德舞者，高祖四年作，以象天下樂己行武以除亂也。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "四年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 7,
        "end": 9
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000108",
    "sentence": "文始舞者，曰本舜招舞也，高祖六年更名曰文始，以示不相襲也。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "六年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 14,
        "end": 16
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000109",
    "sentence": "五行舞者，本周舞也，秦始皇二十六年更名曰五行也。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "二十六年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 13,
        "end": 17
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000110",
    "sentence": "四時舞者，孝文所作，以明示天下之安和也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000111",
    "sentence": "蓋樂己所自作，明有制也；樂先王之樂，明有法也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000112",
    "sentence": "孝景采武德舞以為昭德，以尊大宗廟。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000113",
    "sentence": "至孝宣，采昭德舞為盛德，以尊世宗廟。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000114",
    "sentence": "諸帝廟皆常奏文始、四時、五行舞云。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000115",
    "sentence": "高祖六年又作昭容樂、禮容樂。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "六年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 2,
        "end": 4
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000116",
    "sentence": "昭容者，猶古之昭夏也，主出武德舞。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000117",
    "sentence": "禮容者，主出文始、五行舞。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000118",
    "sentence": "舞人無樂者，將至至尊之前不敢以樂也；出用樂者，言舞不失節，能以樂終也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000119",
    "sentence": "大氐皆因秦舊事焉。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000120",
    "sentence": "初，高祖既定天下，過沛，與故人父老相樂，醉酒歡哀，作「風起」之詩，令沛中僮兒百二十人習而歌之。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "沛",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 10,
        "end": 11
      },
      {
        "text": "沛",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 34,
        "end": 35
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000121",
    "sentence": "至孝惠時，以沛宮為原廟，皆令歌兒習吹以相和，常以百二十人為員。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "沛",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 6,
        "end": 7
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000122",
    "sentence": "文、景之間，禮官肄業而已。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000123",
    "sentence": "至武帝定郊祀之禮，祠太一於甘泉，就乾位也；祭后土於汾陰，澤中方丘也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000124",
    "sentence": "乃立樂府，采詩夜誦，有趙、代、秦、楚之謳。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000125",
    "sentence": "以李延年為協律都尉，多舉司馬相如等數十人造為詩賦，略論律呂，以合八音之調，作十九章之歌。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "司馬",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 12,
        "end": 14
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000126",
    "sentence": "以正月上辛用事甘泉圜丘，使童男女七十人俱歌，昏祠至明。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000127",
    "sentence": "夜常有神光如流星止集于祠壇，天子自竹宮而望拜，百官侍祠者數百人皆肅然動心焉。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000128",
    "sentence": "安世房中歌十七章，其詩曰：",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000129",
    "sentence": "大孝備矣，休德昭清。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000130",
    "sentence": "高張四縣，樂充宮庭。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "高張四縣",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 4
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000131",
    "sentence": "芬樹羽林，雲景杳冥，金支秀華，庶旄翠旌。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000132",
    "sentence": "七始華始，肅倡和聲。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000133",
    "sentence": "神來宴娭，庶幾是聽。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000134",
    "sentence": "粥粥音送，細齊人情。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000135",
    "sentence": "忽乘青玄，熙事備成。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000136",
    "sentence": "清思眑眑，經緯冥冥。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000137",
    "sentence": "我定曆數，人告其心。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000138",
    "sentence": "敕身齊戒，施教申申。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000139",
    "sentence": "乃立祖廟，敬明尊親。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000140",
    "sentence": "大矣孝熙，四極爰轃。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000141",
    "sentence": "王侯秉德，其鄰翼翼，顯明昭式。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000142",
    "sentence": "清明鬯矣，皇帝孝德。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "皇帝",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 5,
        "end": 7
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000143",
    "sentence": "竟全大功，撫安四極。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000144",
    "sentence": "海內有姦，紛亂東北。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000145",
    "sentence": "詔撫成師，武臣承德。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000146",
    "sentence": "行樂交逆，簫、勺群慝。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000147",
    "sentence": "肅為濟哉，蓋定燕國。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000148",
    "sentence": "大海蕩蕩水所歸，高賢愉愉民所懷。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000149",
    "sentence": "大山崔，百卉殖。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000150",
    "sentence": "民何貴？",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000151",
    "sentence": "貴有德。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000152",
    "sentence": "安其所，樂終產。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000153",
    "sentence": "樂終產，世繼緒。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000154",
    "sentence": "飛龍秋，游上天。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000155",
    "sentence": "高賢愉，樂民人。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000156",
    "sentence": "豐草葽，女羅施。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000157",
    "sentence": "殒何如，誰能回！",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000158",
    "sentence": "大莫大，成教德；長莫長，被無極。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000159",
    "sentence": "雷震震，電燿燿。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000160",
    "sentence": "明德鄉，治本約。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "明德鄉",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 3
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000161",
    "sentence": "治本約，澤弘大。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000162",
    "sentence": "加被寵，咸相保。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000163",
    "sentence": "德施大，世曼壽。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000164",
    "sentence": "都荔遂芳，窅窊桂華。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000165",
    "sentence": "孝奏天儀，若日月光。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000166",
    "sentence": "乘玄四龍，回馳北行。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000167",
    "sentence": "羽旄殷盛，芬哉芒芒。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000168",
    "sentence": "孝道隨世，我署文章。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000169",
    "sentence": "桂華。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000170",
    "sentence": "馮馮翼翼，承天之則。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000171",
    "sentence": "吾易久遠，燭明四極。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000172",
    "sentence": "慈惠所愛，美若休德。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000173",
    "sentence": "杳杳冥冥，克綽永福。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000174",
    "sentence": "美芳。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000175",
    "sentence": "磑磑即即，師象山則。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000176",
    "sentence": "烏呼孝哉，案撫戎國。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000177",
    "sentence": "蠻夷竭歡，象來致福。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000178",
    "sentence": "兼臨是愛，終無兵革。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000179",
    "sentence": "嘉薦芳矣，告靈饗矣。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000180",
    "sentence": "告靈既饗，德音孔臧。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000181",
    "sentence": "惟德之臧，建侯之常。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000182",
    "sentence": "承保天休，令問不忘。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000183",
    "sentence": "皇皇鴻明，蕩侯休德。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000184",
    "sentence": "嘉承天和，伊樂厥福。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000185",
    "sentence": "在樂不荒，惟民之則。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000186",
    "sentence": "浚則師德，下民咸殖。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000187",
    "sentence": "令問在舊，孔容翼翼。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000188",
    "sentence": "孔容之常，承帝之明。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000189",
    "sentence": "下民之樂，子孫保光。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000190",
    "sentence": "承順溫良，受帝之光。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000191",
    "sentence": "嘉薦令芳，壽考不忘。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000192",
    "sentence": "承帝明德，師象山則。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000193",
    "sentence": "雲施稱民，永受厥福。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000194",
    "sentence": "承容之常，承帝之明。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000195",
    "sentence": "下民安樂，受福無疆。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000196",
    "sentence": "郊祀歌十九章，其詩曰：",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000197",
    "sentence": "練時日，侯有望，巽膋蕭，延四方。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000198",
    "sentence": "九重開，靈之斿，垂惠恩，鴻祜休。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000199",
    "sentence": "靈之車，結玄雲，駕飛龍，羽旄紛。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000200",
    "sentence": "靈之下，若風馬，左倉龍，右白虎。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000201",
    "sentence": "靈之來，神哉沛，先以雨，般裔裔。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "沛",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 6,
        "end": 7
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000202",
    "sentence": "靈之至，慶陰陰，相放怫，震澹心。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000203",
    "sentence": "靈已坐，五音飭，虞至旦，承靈億。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000204",
    "sentence": "牲繭栗，粢盛香，尊桂酒，賓八鄉。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "賓八鄉",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 12,
        "end": 15
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000205",
    "sentence": "靈安留，吟青黃，遍觀此，眺瑤堂。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000206",
    "sentence": "眾嫭並，綽奇麗，顏如荼，兆逐靡。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000207",
    "sentence": "被華文，廁霧縠，曳阿錫，佩珠玉。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000208",
    "sentence": "俠嘉夜，仂蘭芳，澹容與，獻嘉觴。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000209",
    "sentence": "練時日一",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000210",
    "sentence": "帝臨中壇，四方承宇，繩繩意變，備得其所。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000211",
    "sentence": "清和六合，制數以五。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000212",
    "sentence": "海內安寧，興文匽武。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000213",
    "sentence": "后土富媼，昭明三光。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000214",
    "sentence": "穆穆優游，嘉服上黃。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000215",
    "sentence": "帝臨二",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000216",
    "sentence": "青陽開動，根荄以遂，膏潤并愛，跂行畢逮。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000217",
    "sentence": "霆聲發榮，壧處頃聽，枯槁復產，乃成厥命。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000218",
    "sentence": "眾庶熙熙，施及夭胎，群生啿啿，惟春之祺。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000219",
    "sentence": "青陽三鄒子樂。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000220",
    "sentence": "朱明盛長，归與萬物，桐生茂豫，靡有所詘。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000221",
    "sentence": "敷華就實，既阜既昌，登成甫田，百鬼迪嘗。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000222",
    "sentence": "廣大建祀，肅雍不忘，神若宥之，傳世無疆。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000223",
    "sentence": "朱明四鄒子樂。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000224",
    "sentence": "西顥沆碭，秋氣肅殺，含秀垂穎，續舊不廢。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000225",
    "sentence": "姦偽不萌，祅孽伏息，隅辟越遠，四貉咸服。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000226",
    "sentence": "既畏茲威，惟慕純德，附而不驕，正心翊翊。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000227",
    "sentence": "西顥五鄒子樂。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000228",
    "sentence": "玄冥陵陰，蟄蟲蓋臧，屮木零落，抵冬降霜。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000229",
    "sentence": "易亂除邪，革正異俗，兆民反本，抱素懷樸。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000230",
    "sentence": "條理信義，望禮五嶽。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000231",
    "sentence": "籍斂之時，掩收嘉穀。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000232",
    "sentence": "玄冥六鄒子樂。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000233",
    "sentence": "惟泰元尊，媼神蕃釐，經緯天地，作成四時。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000234",
    "sentence": "精建日月，星辰度理，陰陽五行，周而復始。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000235",
    "sentence": "雲風雷電，降甘露雨，百姓蕃滋，咸循厥緒。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000236",
    "sentence": "繼統共勤，順皇之德，鸞路龍鱗，罔不肸飾。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000237",
    "sentence": "嘉籩列陳，庶幾宴享，滅除凶災，列騰八荒。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000238",
    "sentence": "鐘鼓竽笙，雲舞翔翔，招搖靈旗，九夷賓將。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000239",
    "sentence": "惟泰元七建始元年，丞相匡衡奏罷「鸞路龍鱗」，更定詩曰「涓選休成」。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "元年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 6,
        "end": 8
      },
      {
        "text": "丞相",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 9,
        "end": 11
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000240",
    "sentence": "天地並況，惟予有慕，爰熙紫壇，思求厥路。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000241",
    "sentence": "恭承禋祀，縕豫為紛，黼繡周張，承神至尊。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000242",
    "sentence": "千童羅舞成八溢，合好效歡虞泰一。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000243",
    "sentence": "九歌畢奏斐然殊，鳴琴竽瑟會軒朱。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000244",
    "sentence": "璆磬金鼓，靈其有喜，百官濟濟，各敬厥事。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000245",
    "sentence": "盛牲實俎進聞膏，神奄留，臨須搖。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000246",
    "sentence": "長麗前掞光燿明，寒暑不忒況皇章。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000247",
    "sentence": "展詩應律鋗玉鳴，函宮吐角激徵清。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000248",
    "sentence": "發梁揚羽申以商，造茲新音永久長。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000249",
    "sentence": "聲氣遠條鳳鳥启，神夕奄虞蓋孔享。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000250",
    "sentence": "天地八丞相匡衡奏罷「黼繡周張」，更定詩曰「肅若舊典」。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "丞相",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 3,
        "end": 5
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000251",
    "sentence": "日出入安窮？",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000252",
    "sentence": "時世不與人同。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000253",
    "sentence": "故春非我春，夏非我夏，秋非我秋，冬非我冬。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000254",
    "sentence": "泊如四海之池，遍觀是邪謂何？",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000255",
    "sentence": "吾知所樂，獨樂六龍，六龍之調，使我心若。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000256",
    "sentence": "訾黃其何不徠下！",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000257",
    "sentence": "日出入九",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000258",
    "sentence": "太一況，天馬下，霑赤汗，沬流赭。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000259",
    "sentence": "志俶儻，精權奇，逦浮雲，晻上馳。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000260",
    "sentence": "體容與，迣萬里，今安匹，龍為友。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000261",
    "sentence": "元狩三年馬生渥洼水中作。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "三年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 2,
        "end": 4
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000262",
    "sentence": "天馬徠，從西極，涉流沙，九夷服。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000263",
    "sentence": "天馬徠，出泉水，虎脊兩，化若鬼。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000264",
    "sentence": "天馬徠，歷無草，徑千里，循東道。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000265",
    "sentence": "天馬徠，執徐時，將搖舉，誰與期？",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000266",
    "sentence": "天馬徠，開遠門，竦予身，逝昆侖。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000267",
    "sentence": "天馬徠，龍之媒，游閶闔，觀玉臺。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000268",
    "sentence": "太初四年誅宛王獲宛馬作。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "四年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 2,
        "end": 4
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000269",
    "sentence": "天馬十",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000270",
    "sentence": "天門開，詄蕩蕩，穆並騁，以臨饗。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000271",
    "sentence": "光夜燭，德信著，靈娅平而鴻，長生豫。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000272",
    "sentence": "大朱涂廣，夷石為堂，飾玉梢以舞歌，體招搖若永望。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000273",
    "sentence": "星留俞，塞隕光，照紫幄，珠熉黃。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000274",
    "sentence": "幡比还集，貳雙飛常羊。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000275",
    "sentence": "月穆穆以金波，日華燿以宣明。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000276",
    "sentence": "假清風軋忽，激長至重觴。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000277",
    "sentence": "神裴回若留放，殣冀親以肆章。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000278",
    "sentence": "函蒙祉福常若期，寂漻上天知厥時。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000279",
    "sentence": "泛泛滇滇從高斿，殷勤此路臚所求。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000280",
    "sentence": "佻正嘉吉弘以昌，休嘉砰隱溢四方。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000281",
    "sentence": "專精厲意逝九閡，紛云六幕浮大海。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000282",
    "sentence": "天門十一",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000283",
    "sentence": "景星顯見，信星彪列，象載昭庭，日親以察。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000284",
    "sentence": "參侔開闔，爰推本紀，汾脽出鼎，皇祜元始。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000285",
    "sentence": "五音六律，依韋饗昭，雜變並會，雅聲遠姚。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000286",
    "sentence": "空桑琴瑟結信成，四興遞代八風生。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000287",
    "sentence": "殷殷鐘石羽籥鳴。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000288",
    "sentence": "河龍供鯉醇犧牲。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000289",
    "sentence": "百末旨酒布蘭生。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000290",
    "sentence": "泰尊柘漿析朝酲。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000291",
    "sentence": "微感心攸通修名，周流常羊思所并。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000292",
    "sentence": "穰穰復正直往甯，馮蠵切和疏寫平。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000293",
    "sentence": "上天布施后土成，穰穰豐年四時榮。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000294",
    "sentence": "景星十二元鼎五年得鼎汾陰作。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "五年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 6,
        "end": 8
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000295",
    "sentence": "齊房產草，九莖連葉，宮童效異，披圖案諜。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000296",
    "sentence": "玄氣之精，回復此都，蔓蔓日茂，芝成靈華。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000297",
    "sentence": "齊房十三元封二年芝生甘泉齊房作。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "二年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 6,
        "end": 8
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000298",
    "sentence": "后皇嘉壇，立玄黃服，物發冀州，兆蒙祉福。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "物發冀州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 10,
        "end": 14
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000299",
    "sentence": "沇沇四塞，徦狄合處，經營萬億，咸遂厥宇。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000300",
    "sentence": "后皇十四",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000301",
    "sentence": "華鳞鳞，固靈根。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000302",
    "sentence": "神之斿，過天門，車千乘，敦昆侖。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000303",
    "sentence": "神之出，排玉房，周流雜，拔蘭堂。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000304",
    "sentence": "神之行，旌容容，騎沓沓，般縱縱。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000305",
    "sentence": "神之徠，泛翊翊，甘露降，慶雲集。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000306",
    "sentence": "神之揄，臨壇宇，九疑賓，夔龍舞。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000307",
    "sentence": "神安坐，启吉時，共翊翊，合所思。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000308",
    "sentence": "神嘉虞，申貳觴，福滂洋，邁延長。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000309",
    "sentence": "沛施祐，汾之阿，揚金光，橫泰河，莽若雲，增陽波。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "沛",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 1
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000310",
    "sentence": "遍臚驩，騰天歌。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000311",
    "sentence": "華鳞鳞十五",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000312",
    "sentence": "五神相，包四鄰，土地廣，揚浮雲。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000313",
    "sentence": "扢嘉壇，椒蘭芳，璧玉精，垂華光。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000314",
    "sentence": "益億年，美始興，交於神，若有承。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000315",
    "sentence": "廣宣延，咸畢觴，靈輿位，偃蹇驤。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000316",
    "sentence": "卉汨臚，析奚道？",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000317",
    "sentence": "淫淥澤，鬓然歸。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000318",
    "sentence": "五神十六",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000319",
    "sentence": "朝隴首，覽西垠，剨電抠，獲白麟。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000320",
    "sentence": "爰五止，顯黃德，圖匈虐，熏鬻殛。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000321",
    "sentence": "闢流離，抑不詳，賓百僚，山河饗。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000322",
    "sentence": "掩回轅，鬗長馳，騰雨師，洒路陂。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000323",
    "sentence": "流星隕，感惟風，钆歸雲，撫懷心。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000324",
    "sentence": "朝隴首十七元狩元年行幸雍獲白麟作。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "元年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 7,
        "end": 9
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000325",
    "sentence": "象載瑜，白集西，食甘露，飲榮泉。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000326",
    "sentence": "赤鴈集，六紛員，殊翁雜，五采文。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000327",
    "sentence": "神所見，施祉福，登蓬萊，結無極。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000328",
    "sentence": "象載瑜十八太始三年行幸東海獲赤鴈作。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "三年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 7,
        "end": 9
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000329",
    "sentence": "赤蛟綏，黃華蓋，露夜零，晝晻濭。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000330",
    "sentence": "百君禮，六龍位，勺椒漿，靈已醉。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000331",
    "sentence": "靈既享，錫吉祥，芒芒極，降嘉觴。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000332",
    "sentence": "靈殷殷，爛揚光，延壽命，永未央。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000333",
    "sentence": "杳冥冥，塞六合，澤汪濊，輯萬國。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000334",
    "sentence": "靈禗禗，象輿轙，票然逝，旗逶蛇。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000335",
    "sentence": "禮樂成，靈將歸，託玄德，長無衰。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000336",
    "sentence": "赤蛟十九",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000337",
    "sentence": "其餘巡狩福應之事，不序郊廟，故弗論。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000338",
    "sentence": "是時，河間獻王有雅材，亦以為治道非禮樂不成，因獻所集雅樂。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000339",
    "sentence": "天子下大樂官，常存肄之，歲時以備數，然不常御，常御及郊廟皆非雅聲。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000340",
    "sentence": "然詩樂施於後嗣，猶得有所祖述。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000341",
    "sentence": "昔殷周之雅頌，乃上本有娀、姜原，镨、稷始生，玄王、公劉、古公、大伯、王季、姜女、大任、太姒之德，乃及成湯、文、武受命，武丁、成、康、宣王中興，下及輔佐阿衡、周、召、太公、申伯、召虎、仲山甫之屬，君臣男女有功德者，靡不褒揚。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000342",
    "sentence": "功德既信美矣，褒揚之聲盈乎天地之間，是以光名著於當世，遺譽垂於無窮也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000343",
    "sentence": "今漢郊廟詩歌，未有祖宗之事，八音調均，又不協於鐘律，而內有掖庭材人，外有上林樂府，皆以鄭聲施於朝廷。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000344",
    "sentence": "至成帝時，謁者常山王禹世受可間樂，能說其義，其弟子宋嘱等上書言之，下大夫博士平當等考試。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "大夫",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 34,
        "end": 36
      },
      {
        "text": "博士",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 36,
        "end": 38
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000345",
    "sentence": "當以為「漢承秦滅道之後，賴先帝聖德，博受兼聽，修廢官，立大學，河間獻王聘求幽隱，修興雅樂以助化。時，大儒公孫弘、董仲舒等皆以為音中正雅，立之大樂。春秋鄉射，作於學官，希闊不講。故自公卿大夫觀聽者，但聞鑑鎗，不曉其意，而欲以風諭眾庶，其道無由。是以行之百有餘年，德化至今未成。今嘱等守習孤學，大指歸於興助教化。衰微之學，興廢在人。宜領屬雅樂，以繼絕表微。孔子曰：『人能弘道，非道弘人。』河間區區，不國藩臣，以好學修古，能有所存，民到于今稱之，況於聖主廣被之資，修起舊文，放鄭近雅，述而不作，信而好古，於以風示海內，揚名後世，誠非小功小美也。」事下公卿，以為久遠難分明，當議復寢。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "公孫弘",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 52,
        "end": 55
      },
      {
        "text": "董仲舒",
        "label": "PER",
        "start": 56,
        "end": 59
      },
      {
        "text": "春秋鄉",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 73,
        "end": 76
      },
      {
        "text": "大夫",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 92,
        "end": 94
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000346",
    "sentence": "是時，鄭聲尤甚。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000347",
    "sentence": "黃門名倡丙彊、景武之屬富顯於世，貴戚五侯定陵、富平外戚之家淫侈過度，至與人主爭女樂。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_022_000348",
    "sentence": "哀帝自為定陶王時疾之，又性不好音，及即位，下詔曰：「惟世俗奢泰文巧，而鄭衛之聲興。夫奢泰則下不孫而國貧，文巧則趨末背本者眾，鄭衛之聲興則淫辟之化流，而欲黎庶敦朴家給，猶濁其源而求其清流，豈不難哉！孔子不云乎？『放鄭聲，鄭聲淫。』其罷樂府官。郊祭樂及古兵法武樂，在經非鄭衛之樂者，條奏，別屬他官。」丞相孔光、大司空何武奏：「郊祭樂人員六十二人，給祠南北郊。大樂鼓員六人，嘉至鼓員十人，邯鄲鼓員二人，騎吹鼓員三人，江南鼓員二人，淮南鼓員四人，巴俞鼓員三十六人，歌鼓員二十四人，楚嚴鼓員一人，梁皇鼓員四人，臨淮鼓員三十五人，茲邡鼓員三人，凡鼓十二，員百二十八人，朝賀置酒陳殿下，應古兵法。外郊祭員十三人，諸族樂人兼雲招給祠南郊用六十七人，兼給事雅樂用四人，夜誦員五人，剛、別柎員二人，給盛德主調篪員二人，聽工以律知日冬夏至一人，鐘工、磬工、簫工員各一人，僕射二人主領諸樂人，皆不可罷。竽工員三人，一人可罷。琴工員五人，三人可罷。柱工員二人，一人可罷。繩弦工員六人，四人可罷。鄭四會員六十二人，一人給事雅樂，六十一人可罷。張瑟員八人，七人可罷。安世樂鼓員二十人，十九人可罷。沛吹鼓員十二人，族歌鼓員二十七人，陳吹鼓員十三人，商樂鼓員十四人，東海鼓員十六人，長樂鼓員十三人，縵樂鼓員十三人，凡鼓八，員百二十八人，朝賀置酒，陳前殿房中，不應經法。治竽員五人，楚鼓員六人，常從倡三十人，常從象人四人，詔隨常從倡十六人，秦倡員二十九人，秦倡象人員三人，詔隨秦倡一人，雅大人員九人，朝賀置酒為樂。楚四會員十七人，巴四會員十二人，銚四會員十二人，齊四會員十九人，蔡謳員三人，齊謳員六人，竽瑟鐘磬員五人，皆鄭聲，可罷。師學百四十二人，其七十二人給大官挏馬酒，其七十人可罷。大凡八百二十九人，其三百八十八人不可罷，可領屬大樂，其四百四十一人不應經法，或鄭衛之聲，皆可罷。」奏可。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "丞相",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 148,
        "end": 150
      },
      {
        "text": "沛",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 483,
        "end": 484
      },
      {
        "text": "楚",
        "label": "ORG",
        "start": 639,
